description:
Kanger EVOD 1000 MAH Battery Only

The Kanger EVOD 1000 MaH Battery is great for an all day vape! These small e-cigarettes get nearly 1,000 draws on a single change! Just like the 650's they get around 300 charges in their lifespan!

  • 510 Connection for easy tank swapping
  • 5 Click Easy On/Off Feature
  • Convenient and Compact Size
  • Great all day Vape
  • 3.7 Volt Output
  • Matching Tanks Available
meta_description: Kanger EVOD 1000 MAH Battery is a great battery for people on the go! It also makes a great starter battery for people new to vaping. Try one today!

Kanger EVOD 1000 MAH

Available in Pink, Green, Purple, and Red.

Longer lasting than the 650 MaH, the Kanger EVOD 1000 MaH battery has the same great ease of use and convenience as the 650 MaH. This is a great work vape since it will last all day!

description:
iKit by Eleaf

The Eleaf / iSmoka iKit starter kit is surprisingly good! We weren't sure about this kit because of it's low price point, but it tastes good, has good vapor production, and a good throat hit.

The iKit by Eleaf Includes:

  • 1 Mini BCC Tank
  • 1 Cartomizer Head (coil)
  • 1 Mouth Piece
  • 1 1000 mAh battery (power supply)
  • 1 USB cable charger

Available Colors:

  • Blue
  • Black
  • Pink
  • Silver
meta_description: The iKit by Eleaf pleasantly surprised us. We think you'll like it too. Available in pink, blue, black, and silver. It includes everything you need to start vaping but the e-liquid. Try one today.
name: iKit by Eleaf
short_description:
iKit by Eleaf

This iKit starter kit pleasantly surprised us. The iKit comes with everything but the e-liquid!

Available in Silver, Black, Pink, and Blue

We recommend having at least two batteries when you start vaping. The reason is so that you will have one to vape while the other is charging.

description:
Kanger VV

This Kanger 1000 mAh variable voltage battery is a great all day vape! Variable voltage allows you to fine tune your vaping experience and at 1000 mAh, it lasts all day! These e-cigs go from 3.2V to 4.8V in 0.4V increments. The 510 connection allows you to use almost any tank on the market.

  • 510 Connection allows you to use most tanks
  • 3.2V to 4.8V Variable Voltage
  • 5 Click On/ Off
meta_description: Kanger Variable Voltage E-Cigarette is good for everyone. Beginners and Vaping Enthusiasts alike can enjoy the simplicity and the options that this e-cigarette battery has to offer.
name: Kanger VV 1000mAh
short_description:
Kanger VV

Beginners:
This is a great battery to begin the journey into variable voltage mods. 

Enthusiasts: 
Don't let your fun ruin your expensive mods. Every experience vaper should have one of these for the times when your more expensive mod could break. Varying from 3.2V to 4.8V, it allows you to fine tune your vape without worrying about incurring damage.

description:
Aerotank Mega

Redesigned from the Aerotank, the Kanger Aerotank Mega is offering up some new features!

New Features in the Kanger Aerotank Mega:

  • Larger Tank! 3.8 mL capacity
  • Newly Redesigned Adjustable Airflow controls
  • Includes two tanks- Pyrex already assembled, and a stainless steel replacement.
  • New Coil Design

Same Great Features:

  • Glue-less assembly- all parts are replaceable!
  • 510 connection that fits on most e-cigarette batteries and mods!
  • Bottom Coil Design

name: Aerotank Mega
short_description:
Aerotank Mega

The Aerotank Mega is an upgrade of the Kanger Aerotank! It holds more liquid, has an upgraded airflow valve and coils, and comes with a stainless steel replacement tank! Check out the full description below for additional details!

description:
GeniTank Mini

Every part on this slim little tank is removable and replaceable. There is no glue in this design! Designed to provide a small tank with adjustable airflow, this Kanger Genitank Mini provides a compact design and a great vape. This tank holds 1.5 ml of e-liquid.

Included:
  • Genitank Mini (Including pyrex tank, base, airflow controller, and drip tip
  • 2 Replacement Coils
meta_description: The Kanger Genitank Mini is a small tank with big functionality. Features like adjustable airflow, replaceable parts, dual coil replacement coils, all make this little tank a big winner.
name: GeniTank Mini
short_description:
GeniTank Mini

If you like small tanks that with full functionality, this is the tank for you! The Kanger Genitank Mini has a capacity of only 1.5 ml, but features like adjustable airflow, dual coil replacement coils, and completely replaceable parts allows vapers with smaller mods or eGo style batteries to have the functionality that we all enjoy.

description:
Kanger AeroTank V2

Similar to Kanger's game changer- the Protank, the Aerotank V2 features a couple of upgrades that puts Kanger ahead of the pack again.

The Aerotank V2 features:

  • Adjustable Airflow
  • No Glue- All parts are replaceable
  • 510 Connection means that this will work with almost any battery or mod
  • Pyrex Glass Tank is replaceable and is the same as Protank II and 3.
  • Bottom Coil to avoid dry hits
  • Dual Coil Replacement Coils-
    NOTE: Only interchangeable with Protank 3 Coils. Do not attempt to use Protank or Protank II Coils in this tank!)
  • 2.5 mL capacity

What's Included?

  • Kanger AeroTank
  • Cone (For fitting on smaller batteries)
  • 2 Dual Coil Replacement Coils
meta_description: The Kanger Aerotank is a Protank upgrade with a ton of great features such as: Glueless assembly so all parts are replaceable, adjustable airflow, bottom dual coil replacement coils, and pyrex glass!
name: Kanger AeroTank
short_description:
Kanger AeroTank V2

The Kanger Aerotank V2 has a ton of great features from adjustable airflow to glue-less assembly.  This is a must try item for all vapers!

These coils work on the Aspire Nautilus and Nautilus Mini.

short_description:
The new Aspire Nautilus BVC Coils provide a cleaner vape with larger vapor production! The new engineering also provides more stability than bottom dual coils and a longer life cycle. These bottom vertical coils also accommodate a thicker juice like the 70/30 that many people enjoy!

Aspire recommends that these coils be replaced every 2 weeks (at 500 hits per day).

description:
Nitecore D2 Charger is capable of charging Li-Ion, Ni-MH, and Ni-Cd batteries. Two batteries can charge simultaneously. The display is clear. This charger will also terminate current when charging is complete!

Nitecore D2 Specs and Features

  • LCD displays charging progress, voltage, current, and charging time.
  • Charges two batteries simultaneously
  • Each battery is charged and monitored seperately
  • Designed for best heat dissipation
  • Works with Li-Ion 26650,22650,18650, 17670, 18490, 17500, 18350, 16340
  • Also works with Ni-MH, and Ni-Cd AA, AAA, AAAA, and C rechargeable batteries.
  • Optimized for IMR Batteries
  • Circuitry detects battery and status before charging to accurately determine optimal voltage and charge mode.
  • Overcharge Protection.
  • Temperature Monitoring to prevent overheating
  • Made from durable, flame resistant, fire retardant ABS.
  • Reverse Polarity Protection
name: Nitecore D2 Charger
short_description: Nitecore D2 Charger can charge two batteries simultaneously. The LCD displays all necessary information, and the auto power function even stops the current when charging is complete. Read the description below for more details.

  • 510 Connection

Kanger VV

This Kanger 1000 mAh variable voltage battery is a great all day vape! Variable voltage allows you to fine tune your vaping experience and at 1000 mAh, it lasts all day! These e-cigs go from 3.2V to 4.8V in 0.4V increments. The 510 connection allows you to use almost any tank on the market.

  • 510 Connection allows you to use most tanks
  • 3.2V to 4.8V Variable Voltage

short_description:
Kanger VV

Beginners:
This is a great battery to begin the journey into variable voltage mods. 

Enthusiasts: 
Don't let your fun ruin your expensive mods. Every experience vaper should have one of these for the times when your more expensive mod could break. Varying from 3.2V to 4.8V, it allows you to fine tune your vape without worrying about incurring damage.
